250
00:13:32,976 --> 00:13:35,764
10 major earthquakes have hit Afghanistan.

251
00:13:35,764 --> 00:13:39,490
Thousands of people have been displaced or have lost their lives.

252
00:13:39,490 --> 00:13:43,412
And the most extreme earthquake hit last month, on 7th October.

253
00:13:43,412 --> 00:13:46,645
"The death toll from an earthquake in Western Afghanistan 

254
00:13:46,645 --> 00:13:50,371
has risen to around 320 
with 1,000 more injured."

255
00:13:50,588 --> 00:13:53,998
This is why the biggest cricket star in Afghanistan, Rashid Khan, 

256
00:13:53,998 --> 00:14:01,235
donated his entire tournament fees from 
this World Cup to the earthquake victims.

257
00:14:01,235 --> 00:14:04,909
He says that people pray for them back home. 

258
00:14:04,909 --> 00:14:08,568
They watch their matches hoping that they will win.

259
00:14:08,568 --> 00:14:12,830
Because cricket is now the only source of joy in Afghanistan. 

260
00:14:12,830 --> 00:14:16,577
The restrictions Taliban has placed on women,

261
00:14:16,577 --> 00:14:18,785
and the atrocities committed by them,

262
00:14:18,785 --> 00:14:21,756
hardly any place on Earth is as restrictive as it is.

263
00:14:21,756 --> 00:14:23,873
Women are confined to their homes

264
00:14:23,873 --> 00:14:27,674
and prohibited from working or studying,

265
00:14:27,674 --> 00:14:31,243
Thankfully, Afghanistan's men's cricket team has the opportunity

266
00:14:31,243 --> 00:14:33,467
to participate in the World Cup.

267
00:14:33,467 --> 00:14:36,296
However, the women's cricket team

268
00:14:36,296 --> 00:14:38,908
is now refugees in Australia,

269
00:14:38,908 --> 00:14:42,151
they are still struggling in their pursuit of playing opportunities.

270
00:14:42,151 --> 00:14:48,453
Last year, Rashid Khan expressed solidarity with 
the daughters and sisters of Afghanistan,

271
00:14:48,453 --> 00:14:55,598
advocating for the reversal of the decision 
to ban girls from high schools and universities.

272
00:14:55,598 --> 00:14:58,112
"Every day of education wasted,

273
00:14:58,112 --> 00:15:01,103
is a day wasted from the future of the country."

274
00:15:01,103 --> 00:15:04,542
For Afghani cricketers, cricket is not merely a sport.

275
00:15:04,542 --> 00:15:07,449
This is a means to fight the circumstances.

276
00:15:07,449 --> 00:15:11,599
Sometimes against the Soviet invasion.
sometimes against Taliban's oppressions.

277
00:15:11,599 --> 00:15:15,957
The Afghani players do not hesitate to express their opinions.

278
00:15:15,957 --> 00:15:18,491
Last month, after defeating Pakistan,

279
00:15:18,491 --> 00:15:20,633
the team celebrated the victory.

280
00:15:20,633 --> 00:15:23,639
Afghan Captain Hasmatullah Shahidi

281
00:15:23,639 --> 00:15:27,176
dedicated the victory to Afghan refugees,

282
00:15:27,176 --> 00:15:31,674
particularly those escaping Taliban 
rule and seeking refuge in Pakistan.

283
00:15:31,674 --> 00:15:35,577
Whom Pakistan is forcefully sending back to Afghanistan. 

284
00:15:35,577 --> 00:15:38,837
"Islamabad has ordered all undocumented immigrants,

285
00:15:38,837 --> 00:15:42,511
which includes around 1.7 million Afghan nationals,

286
00:15:42,511 --> 00:15:43,722
to leave the country."

287
00:15:43,722 --> 00:15:47,129
The game of cricket emerges as 
a potential avenue for diplomatic relations.

288
00:15:47,532 --> 00:15:51,085
When Afghanistan attained full membership in the ICC,

289
00:15:51,085 --> 00:15:58,004
their inaugural test match was against India in Bangalore.

290
00:15:58,004 --> 00:16:01,450
The Afghanistani President Ashraf Ghani was invited to India

291
00:16:01,450 --> 00:16:03,561
to watch this first test match.

292
00:16:03,561 --> 00:16:05,828
Similarly, during the 2011 World Cup,

293
00:16:05,828 --> 00:16:11,495
Dr Manmohan Singh extended an invitation to 
then Pakistani Prime Minister Yusuf Raza Gilani

294
00:16:11,495 --> 00:16:13,913
to watch the India v. Pakistan match,

295
00:16:13,913 --> 00:16:17,384
aiming to ease tensions between the two countries.

296
00:16:17,384 --> 00:16:20,782
A similar initiative occurred in 2004 when

297
00:16:20,782 --> 00:16:23,207
the Indian cricket team visited Pakistan,

298
00:16:23,207 --> 00:16:25,736
leading both nations to relax visa regulations,

299
00:16:25,736 --> 00:16:29,771
allowing the public to attend matches in these countries.

300
00:16:29,771 --> 00:16:33,253
These instances underscore the profound impact of cricket's popularity

301
00:16:33,253 --> 00:16:36,849
in fostering positive relations globally.

302
00:16:36,849 --> 00:16:41,438
Consequently, there is a need to promote this sport in other countries,

303
00:16:41,438 --> 00:16:45,541
encouraging both small and large 
nations to take an interest in cricket.

304
00:16:45,541 --> 00:16:49,921
Unfortunately, the current state of the sport

305
00:16:49,921 --> 00:16:52,642
reveals a concentration of control in 
the hands of only three major countries,

306
00:16:53,200 --> 00:16:56,233
with India holding the strongest influence.

307
00:16:56,233 --> 00:17:00,243
While the ICC theoretically comprises 12 full members

308
00:17:00,243 --> 00:17:02,069
and 94 associate countries,

309
00:17:02,069 --> 00:17:04,281
this is just the theoritical model.

310
00:17:04,281 --> 00:17:05,799
The practical reality is that ICC

311
00:17:05,799 --> 00:17:13,261
is controlled by the BCCI, England and Wales Cricket Board (ECB), and Cricket Australia (CA).

312
00:17:13,261 --> 00:17:16,614
These three nations are often referred to as the Big Three.

313
00:17:16,614 --> 00:17:19,708
The consolidation of power escalated after February 2014 when

314
00:17:19,708 --> 00:17:23,138
the ICC implemented structural and financial reforms,

315
00:17:23,138 --> 00:17:26,089
granting India, England, and Australia nearly

316
00:17:26,089 --> 00:17:28,291
complete control over cricket's governance.

317
00:17:28,291 --> 00:17:33,760
This power shift extended to the Big Three controlling the flow of money.

318
00:17:33,760 --> 00:17:37,646
Out of ICC's total projected gross revenue of $2.5 billion,

319
00:17:37,646 --> 00:17:43,709
the BCCI received a significant share of $570 million or 22.8%.

320
00:17:43,709 --> 00:17:48,146
England and Australia obtained $143 million and $132 million,

321
00:17:48,146 --> 00:17:50,727
constituting 5.7% and 5.2% shares, respectively.

322
00:17:50,727 --> 00:17:54,857
This distribution left associate members with minimal financial support.

323
00:17:54,857 --> 00:18:00,728
The Big Three argued that the funds invested in 
cricket development in associate countries

324
00:18:00,728 --> 00:18:03,034
did not yield satisfactory returns,

325
00:18:03,034 --> 00:18:05,219
prompting a reduction in financial support.

326
00:18:05,219 --> 00:18:09,236
Fortunately, in 2017, this model was repealed,

327
00:18:09,236 --> 00:18:10,821
and a new model was introduced.

328
00:18:10,821 --> 00:18:12,892
When the voting took place for the new model,

329
00:18:12,892 --> 00:18:15,965
13 votes were in favour, and only one vote dissented,

330
00:18:15,965 --> 00:18:18,572
this dissenting vote was cast by the BCCI.

331
00:18:18,572 --> 00:18:19,552
Why?

332
00:18:19,552 --> 00:18:20,758
Because, under this new model,

333
00:18:20,758 --> 00:18:26,574
BCCI's share would be reduced from $570 million to $293 million.

334
00:18:26,574 --> 00:18:30,259
A share cut from 22% to 11%.

335
00:18:30,259 --> 00:18:32,505
Concurrently, associate countries were

336
00:18:32,505 --> 00:18:34,642
allocated $280 million

337
00:18:34,642 --> 00:18:38,645
to stimulate growth in cricket in regions where

338
00:18:38,645 --> 00:18:40,716
the sport isn't very popular yet.

339
00:18:40,716 --> 00:18:43,581
Regrettably, this model endured for only six years.

340
00:18:43,581 --> 00:18:45,752
This year, another model was passed,

341
00:18:45,752 --> 00:18:51,105
granting BCCI complete financial control over international cricket.

342
00:18:51,105 --> 00:18:54,246
In July, the ICC approved a new revenue system,

343
00:18:54,246 --> 00:18:58,957
where full members will receive an 88.8% share of revenue

344
00:18:58,957 --> 00:19:01,654
between 2024 and 2027.

345
00:19:01,654 --> 00:19:04,238
Over the next three years, ICC's earnings are expected to be

346
00:19:04,238 --> 00:19:07,103
around $600 million annually,

347
00:19:07,103 --> 00:19:10,954
with BCCI receiving $230 million.

348
00:19:10,954 --> 00:19:13,337
Around 38.5%.

349
00:19:13,337 --> 00:19:18,058
The associate teams would receive 11% combined.

350
00:19:18,058 --> 00:19:20,233
And the other full members

351
00:19:20,233 --> 00:19:23,053
would get a share in the single digits.

352
00:19:23,053 --> 00:19:25,390
The rationale behind this new revenue system is

353
00:19:25,390 --> 00:19:27,154
the same as the one in 2014

354
00:19:27,154 --> 00:19:31,174
that BCCI significantly contributes commercially to cricket.

355
00:19:31,174 --> 00:19:35,798
Given that most advertisers and the IPL are India-centric, 

356
00:19:35,798 --> 00:19:39,433
85% of commercial weightage is attributed to BCCI.

357
00:19:39,433 --> 00:19:43,777
This signifies that BCCI's contribution to the 
cricket economy ranges from 70% to 80%.

358
00:19:43,777 --> 00:19:48,211
Notably, the biggest contributor to this cricket economy is the IPL,

359
00:19:48,211 --> 00:19:50,409
commonly referred to as the Cash Cow.

360
